<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%= title || 'Iniciar Sesión - Perfil Humano Digital' %></title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: #eaf0f6;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 1100px;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 24px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
    }

    .left-panel {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1da1f2, #22c55e);
      color: white;
      padding: 28px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .image-box {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .image-box img {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 460px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      display: block;
    }

    .left-panel h2 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      color: #0f172a;
    }

    .left-panel p,
    .left-panel li {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .left-panel ul {
      margin-top: 12px;
      padding-left: 22px;
    }

    .right-panel {
      padding: 48px 36px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .right-panel h1 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .subtitle {
      color: #6b7280;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .alert {
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .alert-error {
      background: #fee2e2;
      color: #b91c1c;
    }

    .alert-success {
      background: #dcfce7;
      color: #166534;
    }

    label {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #111827;
    }

    input {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      outline: none;
    }

    input:focus {
      border-color: #2563eb;
    }

    button {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 15px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #2563eb;
      color: white;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    button:hover {
      background: #1d4ed8;
    }

    .bottom-link {
      margin-top: 18px;
      color: #4b5563;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .bottom-link a {
      color: #2563eb;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .bottom-link a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .wrapper {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .left-panel,
      .right-panel {
        padding: 28px;
      }

      .left-panel h2 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
      }

      .right-panel h1 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="left-panel">
      <div class="image-box">
        <img src="/images/perfil-humano-digital.png" alt="Perfil Humano Digital" />
      </div>

      <h2>Continúa tu Perfil Humano Digital</h2>
      <p>Inicia sesión para acceder a tu cuestionario y seguir construyendo tu Perfil Humano Digital.</p>

      <ul>
        <li>Tu progreso se guarda automáticamente.</li>
        <li>Puedes continuar donde te quedaste.</li>
        <li>Tus respuestas son confidenciales.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="right-panel">
      <h1>Iniciar sesión</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Ingresa tus datos para acceder a la plataforma.</p>

      <% if (error) { %>
        <div class="alert alert-error"><%= error %></div>
      <% } %>

      <% if (message) { %>
        <div class="alert alert-success"><%= message %></div>
      <% } %>

      <form action="/login" method="POST">
        <label for="email">Correo electrónico</label>
        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required />

        <label for="password">Contraseña</label>
        <input type="password" id="password" name="password" required />

        <button type="submit">Entrar</button>
      </form>

      <p class="bottom-link">
        ¿No tienes cuenta? <a href="/register">Regístrate aquí</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>